      "description": "[Accurate Prediction, Locking on to Transiting Satellites]\nBased on the professional SGP4 algorithm, satellite orbits and transit times are calculated in real time. Clear azimuth, elevation, and pointing guidance is provided for both LEO and GEO satellites, allowing you to easily establish satellite connections.\n\n[AI Recognition, Automatic Call Log Transfer]\nInnovatively integrated AI voice recognition technology! With a single click, recording automatically extracts key information like callsign and QTH, generating a standard contact log for you, completely hands-free.\n\n[Essential Exam Prep, Continuously Updated Question Bank]\nContains the latest question banks for Amateur Radio Class A/B/C certifications, along with practice exams and question-review tools to help you efficiently review and successfully obtain your certification.\n\n[Professional Management, Clear and Organized Records]\nA powerful log management system supports Maidenhead grid positioning. All contact records and voice logs are quickly searchable, helping you become a more professional HAM.",
